_:Na6549f83584b47cdac9bb303d617f47a <http://schema.org/description> "<p>The Rt Hon Darren Jones MP was appointed Chancellor of the Duchy of Lancaster on 5 September 2025, Minister for Intergovernmental Relations on 6 September 2025 and Chief Secretary to the Prime Minister at the Cabinet Office on 1 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>He was previously Chief Secretary to the Treasury.</p>\n\n<p>He was elected as the MP for Bristol North West in June 2017.</p>\n" .
